What is AWS CodeDeploy?

AWS CodeDeploy automates application deployment to servers such as:

Amazon EC2
On-premises servers
AWS Lambda
Amazon ECS

Think of it like this:

GitHub
   │
   ▼
CodeBuild
   │
Creates artifact
   │
   ▼
CodeDeploy
   │
Deploys artifact
   ▼
EC2 Servers

CodeBuild creates the application.

CodeDeploy installs it on servers.
